---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const gumroadUrl = 'https://ulysis.gumroad.com/l/rlmsco';
---

<BaseLayout title="SocialScheduler AI - Right-click to Share Any Page" description="AI-powered Chrome extension that lets you right-click any webpage and instantly share it to Twitter/X or LinkedIn with AI-rewritten content.">
  
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
        🚀 New Chrome Extension
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Share Any Page in <span class="text-blue-600">One Click</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Right-click any webpage → AI rewrites it for your platform → Post to Twitter or LinkedIn instantly.
        No more copying, pasting, and formatting.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="{chromeStoreUrl}" 
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-xl text-lg font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z"/>
          </svg>
          Add to Chrome — <span class="font-bold">Free</span>
        </a>
        <a href="{gumroadUrl}" 
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-xl text-lg font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
          🚀 Upgrade to Pro — $9/mo
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-3">Free plan: 5 posts/month. No credit card required.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Demo / How it works -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Right-Click</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Right-click any webpage, article, or link. Choose "Share to Twitter" or "Share to LinkedIn" from the menu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">AI Rewrites</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Our AI reads the page, extracts the key information, and rewrites it as an engaging social media post tailored to each platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-100 text-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Post Instantly</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Review, edit if needed, and publish. Zero context switching between reading and sharing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Features</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-2xl">📎</div>
          <div><strong>Right-Click from Any Page</strong><br/><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">No need to copy URLs. Just right-click and share.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-2xl">🤖</div>
          <div><strong>AI Writing Engine</strong><br/><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Auto-generates platform-optimized posts from page content.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-2xl">✏️</div>
          <div><strong>Edit Before Posting</strong><br/><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">AI drafts, you polish. Full control over your voice.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-2xl">🔗</div>
          <div><strong>Auto URL Embedding</strong><br/><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">The page link is always included in every post.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-2xl">🔒</div>
          <div><strong>Your API Key, Your Data</strong><br/><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">We never see your content. Everything stays in your browser.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-2xl">📊</div>
          <div><strong>Post History</strong><br/><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Track everything you've shared. Review and manage from the popup.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Pricing</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Free</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">$0</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ 5 posts per month</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ Twitter / X posting</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ LinkedIn posting</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ AI rewriting</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ Post history</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="{chromeStoreUrl}" class="block w-full py-2.5 text-center bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-lg font-medium">
            Add to Chrome Free
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border-2 border-blue-500 relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 right-4 px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs rounded-full font-medium">Popular</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Pro</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">$9<span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">/month</span></p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ Unlimited posts</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ Twitter / X posting</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ LinkedIn posting</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ AI rewriting (unlimited)</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ Multiple post variants</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">✓ Priority support</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="{gumroadUrl}" class="block w-full py-2.5 text-center bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-lg font-medium">
            Upgrade Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">FAQ</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">Do I need an API key?</summary>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Yes, but you can use your own OpenAI or DeepSeek API key. Your data never leaves your browser. We don't charge API fees — you only pay if you upgrade to Pro for unlimited posts.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">Is there a free plan?</summary>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Yes! 5 posts per month free. Add your own API key and try it with zero risk.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">Which platforms are supported?</summary>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Currently Twitter / X and LinkedIn. More platforms (Bluesky, Mastodon, Threads) coming soon.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">Is my data private?</summary>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Absolutely. Everything runs in your browser. Your API key and social tokens are stored locally in Chrome. We have zero access to your content.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
